一种可以满足你对麸皮需求的干麦片。味道独特，像葡萄干和盐。
一根美味、金色、肥美的棍子。
美味，金黄，棍子上的肥美脂肪。
一块又小又甜的巧克力。
如果你想知道空气从哪里来……
音乐水果放在一个稍微少一些音乐的容器里。
只是一罐熟透的桃子在自己的果汁中畅游。
一罐优质的圣马扎诺番茄，产自意大利南部山区。
A small can of pine nuts. Can be eaten on their own, if you're into that.

一块看起来很像巧克力的方形条状物，用一种难以形容的灰色的包装纸包装。以前确实曾救过士兵的命——但通常是通过挡住子弹的方式。
悬浮在硬糖中的一群蚂蚁。那些东西都死了，对吧？
The first pet food product that is made fully sustainable by employing ancient British animal husbandry techniques.
A combination of firm cheese, salt, herbs, garlic, oil, and pine nuts. Frequently used as a sauce for pasta or pizza, or eaten on bread.
番茄酱，披萨饼或意大利面的完美选择。妈妈咪呀！
A classic white sauce common to several European cultures.
A blackened, blistered bell pepper. Great for making sauces.

A quick Donk-dinner, now with flavour! And it's even hot!
Neon-orange mac n' cheese in seconds!
Neon-orange mac n' cheese, ready to eat!
Donk Co's signature Donkhiladas with Donk sauce, for an 'authentic' taste of Mexico.
Donk Co's signature Donkhiladas with Donk sauce, served as hot as the Mexican sun.
A dumpling made by wrapping unleavened dough around a savoury or sweet filling and cooking in boiling water. This one is filled with a potato and onion mixture.
A savoury mixture of ground meat and rice wrapped in cooked cabbage leaves and topped with a tomato sauce. To die for.
用来做寿司的干海草片。在它上面放上配料以开始制作定制寿司！
A dried mixture of oats, nuts, fruits, and chocolate condensed into a chewy bar. Makes a great snack while space-hiking.
A ball of cooked rice surrounding a filling formed into a triangular shape and wrapped in seaweed. Can be added fillings!
A ball of cooked rice surrounding a filling formed into a triangular shape and wrapped in seaweed.
A creamy serving of mashed potatoes, a staple of many Thanksgiving dinners.
A traditional Brazilian treat made of ground peanuts, sugar, and salt compressed into a cylinder.
略微皱缩的深色黄瓜。闻起来有点酸，但令人难以置信的诱人。
一盘新鲜蔬菜被半透明的米纸包裹着，再配上甜辣椒酱。你要么爱它们，要么恨它们。
A Waffle Co. brand gorilla cube. Now with extra molecules!
A new Nanotrasen classic, the chicken cube. Tastes like everything!
我们本以为它是个好主意。只需加水。
作为蛾类菜肴的主食，奶酪经常被添加各种风味，以保持其饮食的多样性。药草就是这样一个补充，并且特别受欢迎。
正如阿尔顿勋爵所言，全世界99.997%的烤奶酪食谱完全是谎言：奶酪从来没有被烤过，它只是一个含有融化奶酪的烤三明治。另一方面，这是，一个真正的烤奶酪，包括烤痕等等。
包含卷心菜、红洋葱和番茄的普通沙拉。可以作为制作一百万种沙拉的完美基础。
虽然烘烤过的种子远不能填饱肚子，但在蛾子中，它是一种很受欢迎的小吃。盐、糖，甚至一些更具异国情调的调味品都可以加，以增加风味。
这是一种为飞蛾舰队的工程师们准备的常见零食，由种子、坚果、巧克力、爆米花和薯片制成，其设计具有高热量，并且在需要额外补充营养时易于食用的特点。
A strong, glutenous dough, made with cornmeal and flour, designed to hold up to cheese and sauce.
A mothic classic made with cheese curds and tofu (amongst other things). Translated literally the name means 'squeaking stir fry', a name given due to the distinctive squeak of the proteins.
Grilled cheese and salad in a cabbage wrap, topped with delicious sweet chili sauce.

What's better than cheese curds? Deep fried cheese curds! What's better than deep fried cheese curds? Deep fried cheese curds with chili (and more cheese) on top! And what's better than that? Putting it on fries!
一个烤奶酪轮，融汁四溢而美味
A baked cheese wheel: a mothic favourite for sharing. Usually served with crispy bread slices for dipping, because the only thing better than good cheese is good cheese on bread.
A fine lasagne made with pesto and a herby white sauce, ready to bake. Good for multiple servings.
A fine lasagne made with pesto and a herby white sauce. Good for multiple servings.
A slice of herby, pesto-y lasagne.
A big pan of layered potatoes topped with rice and vegetable stock, ready to be baked into a delicious sharing meal.

A mothic favourite, baked rice can be filled with a variety of vegetable fillings to make a delicious meal to share. Potatoes are also often layered on the bottom of the cooking vessel to create a flavourful crust which is hotly contested amongst diners.
A single portion of baked rice, perfect as a side dish, or even as a full meal.
A cob of corn, baked in the roasting heat of an oven until it blisters and blackens. Beloved as a quick yet flavourful and filling component for dishes on the Fleet.
What's better than baked corn? Baked corn with butter!
Sweet, spicy, saucy, and all kinds of corny.
Sliced vegetables with a roasted pepper sauce. Delicious, for a peasant food.
The perfect dish to save your restaurant from a vindictive food critic. Bonus points if you've got a rat in your hat.
Little sticks of mozzarella, breaded and fried.
A pepper with the top removed and a herby cheese and onion mix stuffed inside. Probably shouldn't be eaten raw.
A soft yet still crisp bell pepper, with a wonderful melty cheesy interior.

A dish made from fried vegetables, popular amongst fueljacks- the brave moths who operate the fuel skimmers to keep the fleet running. Given the constant need for fuel, and the limited windows in which the stars align for harvesting (literally), they'll often take packed meals to save on trips to the mess, which they heat using the fresh canisters.
Fried balls of macaroni cheese dipped in corn batter, served with tomato sauce. A popular snack across the galaxy, and especially on the Mothic Fleet- where they tend to use Ready-Donk as the base.

The PSB, or Prepacked Sustenance Bar, is a densely packed, nutrient rich food which is designed to hold the populace over during times of food shortage. Made from soy and pea protein, each lasts 3 days if adequately rationed. While they have a long shelf life, they do eventually go bad- prompting them to be sold as surplus by the fleet. This particular one is, like most artificially-flavoured moth food, mixed-herb flavoured.

The PSB, or Prepacked Sustenance Bar, is a densely packed, nutrient rich food which is designed to hold the populace over during times of food shortage. Made from soy and pea protein, each lasts 3 days if adequately rationed. While they have a long shelf life, they do eventually go bad- prompting them to be sold as surplus by the fleet. This particular one is neapolitan flavoured- strawberry, vanilla, and chocolate.

The PSB, or Prepacked Sustenance Bar, is a densely packed, nutrient rich food which is designed to hold the populace over during times of food shortage. Made from soy and pea protein, each lasts 3 days if adequately rationed. While they have a long shelf life, they do eventually go bad- prompting them to be sold as surplus by the fleet. This particular one is three-cheese flavoured- parmesan, mozzarella, and cheddar.
surplus fleet PSB- mint choc chip flavour

The PSB, or Prepacked Sustenance Bar, is a densely packed, nutrient rich food which is designed to hold the populace over during times of food shortage. Made from soy and pea protein, each lasts 3 days if adequately rationed. While they have a long shelf life, they do eventually go bad- prompting them to be sold as surplus by the fleet. surplus fleet PSB- three course dinner

The PSB, or Prepacked Sustenance Bar, is a densely packed, nutrient rich food which is designed to hold the populace over during times of food shortage. Made from soy and pea protein, each lasts 3 days if adequately rationed. While they have a long shelf life, they do eventually go bad- prompting them to be sold as surplus by the fleet. This particular one is split into three flavours, making up a typical meal- tomato soup, roast pumpkin, and blueberry pie.
A soup made from raw cotton in a flavourful vegetable broth. Enjoyed only by moths and the criminally tasteless.
A simple and filling soup made from homemade cheese and sweet potato. The curds provide texture while the whey provides volume- and they both provide deliciousness!
A seed based soup, made by germinating seeds and then boiling them. Produces a particularly bitter broth which is usually balanced by the addition of vinegar.
For the hombres who don't want carne.
A spicy bean stew with lots of veggies, commonly served aboard the fleet as a filling and satisfying meal with rice or bread.
A hearty oat stew, prepared with oats, sweet potatoes, and various winter vegetables.
Tömpröttkrakklmæsch, or heartburn soup, is a cold soup dish that originated amongst the jungle moths, and is named for two things- its rosy pink colour, and its scorchingly hot chilli heat.
A plate of rice porridge. It's mostly flavourless, but it does fill a spot. To the Chinese it's congee, and moths call it höllflöfmisklsløsk.
Nobody is quite sure why this smiley bowl of rice porridge with eggs and bacon is named after a mythological Chinese figure- it's just sorta what it's always been called.
Commonly served aboard the mothic fleet, rice porridge with töchtaüse syrup is more palatable than the regular stuff, if even just because it's spicier than normal.
A plate of cornmeal porridge. It's more flavourful than most porridges, and makes a good base for other flavours, too.
A rich and creamy bowl of cheesy cornmeal porridge.
Polenta loaded with cheese, served with a few discs of fried eggplant and some tomato sauce. Lække!

While it's far from an original creation of the moths, caprese salad has become a favourite aboard the Fleet due to how simple it is to prepare yet how tasty it is. To the moths it's known as zaileskenknusksolt: two tone salad, in GalCom.

Lörtonknusksolt, or Fleet Salad in GalCom, is commonly seen at the snack bars and canteens aboard the Fleet. The grilled cheese makes it particularly filling, while the croutons provide a crunchy kick.
A salad with added cotton and a basic dressing. Presumably either moths are around, or the South's risen again.
Originally a Kenyan recipe, kachumbari is yet another cross-cultural favourite from humanity that has been adopted by the moths- though some ingredients have been necessarily changed.
Another human classic adopted by the moths, mothic pizza is characterised by the use of fresh ingredients, particularly fresh mozzarella, and the use of strong flour to produce a glutenous dough.
A key characteristic of mothic pizza is that it's sold by weight- single slices are available for discretionary credits, while a meal ticket can buy a whole pie.
A slice of mothic margherita pizza, the most humble of pizzas.
A favourite amongst the more adventurous moths, firecracker pizza is HOT HOT HOT!
They're not kidding when they call this a hot pizza pie.
A spicy slice of something quite nice.
For centuries, scholars have asked: how much cheese is too much cheese?
A favourite amongst mice, rats, and English inventors.
It's the cheesiest slice in the galaxy!
为讨厌番茄的人做的披萨。
You say to-may-to, I say to-mah-to, and we put neither on this pizza.
Pesto is a popular pizza topping for moths, quite possibly because it exemplifies their favourite flavours: cheese, herbs, and veggies.
Green as the grass in the garden. Not that there's many of those on mothic ships.
A slice of presto pesto pizza.
啊，大蒜。一种广受欢迎的配料，可能吸血鬼除外。

A chunk of crispy, cowboy-style cornbread. Consume contentedly.

Ælorölen (cheese balls) are a traditional mothic dessert, made of soft cheese, powdered sugar and flour, rolled into balls, battered and then deep fried. They're often served with either chocolate sauce or honey, or sometimes both!
A light and fluffy vegan marshmallow flavoured with vanilla and rum and topped with soft chocolate. These are known to the moths as höllflöfstarkken: cloud squares.
Fluffy little clouds of joy- in a strangely moth-like colour.
Red porridge with yoghurt. The name and vegetable ingredients obscure the sweet nature of the dish, which is commonly served as a dessert aboard the fleet.
A rubbery strip of gum. It's stamped with the emblem of the Mothic Nomad Fleet.

Stay awake during long shifts in the maintenance tunnels with Activin! The approval seal of the Mothic Nomad Fleet is emblazoned on the packaging, alongside a litany of health and safety disclaimers in both Mothic and Galactic Common.
Spacer's Sidekick: Breathe easy with a friend at your side!
蓬松的薄饼。华夫饼更柔软的长辈。
一种几乎没有煮熟的食物，有些人可能会误认为是煎饼。它渴望得到煎锅。
一块松软可口的巧克力碎片松饼.
A fat stack of fluffy pancakes!
A grand tower of fluffy, delicious pancakes!

美味而松软的小蛋糕，点缀有浆果

Microwave is taken by a fey mood! It has cooked an exceptional plump helmet biscuit!
Just like your little sister used to make.
A sugar cookie in the shape of a [shape]. I hope Santa likes it!

美味又有嚼劲的花生曲奇。

一块没切开的布朗尼蛋糕，用刀切！
一块方形的美味、耐嚼的布朗尼。通常是瘾君子的目标。
一个简单的馅饼，但不影响它的美味。
就像回到家一样，在小丑星球上！嘟嘟！
没有黑鸟，这是一个好迹象。

味道是如此的好，能让一个成年人哭。

一种由巧克力制成的可口甜点，有一个液体核心。
An odd blue pie made with toxic blumpkin.
A slice of blumpkin pie, with whipped cream on top. Is this edible?
A delicious jelly made with sweet potatoes.
A slice of sweet dulce de batata jelly.
A delightful healthy snack made of nut layers with thin bread.
A portion of a delightful healthy snack made of nut layers with thin bread
A decadent pie made of a creamy chocolate mousse filling topped with a layer of whipped cream and chocolate shavings. Sliceable.
A slice of french silk pie, filled with a chocolate mousse and topped with a layer of whipped cream and chocolate shavings. Delicious enough to make you cry.
一盘在奶油土豆泥下烘烤的肉末和混合蔬菜，可以切开。
一片切割得比较马虎的牧羊人派，由切碎的肉和混合蔬菜在一层奶油土豆泥下烘烤而成，危险的非凡美味啊。
A slice of the most cheezy pizza in galaxy.
也许这是你生命中的最后一片披萨。
在制作这个披萨饼的过程中，没有一个番茄人受到伤害。

富含细菌的发霉披萨片
这种曾经美味的比萨饼不仅表面覆盖着一层喷发孢子的真菌，而且在无人看管的情况下，它似乎会移动和滑动，充满新的生命。

Probably too incredible for mortal men to fully enjoy.
上面有苹果的美味沙拉。

每个人都喜欢米饭布丁！
证明意大利人掌握了每一种碳水化合物。
A salad brimming with untapped potential.
A spicy and savory meat and rice dish.

A healthy kale salad drizzled in oil, perfect for warm summer months.
一种广受欢迎的沙拉，由番茄、洋葱、羊乳酪和橄榄做成，都淋上橄榄油。虽然感觉好像还缺了什么.......
A simple yet flavorful salad of onions, lettuce, croutons, and shreds of cheese dressed in oil. Comes with a slice of pita bread!
一份简单的胡萝卜、生菜和豌豆沙拉，淋上少许盐和油。
一盘煮熟的土豆，混合了煮蛋、洋葱和蛋黄酱。是每一次有自尊烧烤的主食。
一种充满活力的水果沙拉，由菠菜、浆果和菠萝块淋上油制成。好吃！
意大利沙拉一种传统的意大利沙拉，由意大利腊肠、马苏里拉奶酪、橄榄和西红柿制成。通常作为第一道菜的餐点。
用肉、奶酪、面包和几片生菜叶做成的宏伟杰作！亚瑟·登特会为你骄傲的。
一种温暖、融化的三明治，与番茄汤完美搭配。
暖和的一天吃些清淡的小吃，……但如果你把它烤了呢？
你希望有一些花生酱来配这个……
这似乎有些问题，你不太明白问题出在哪了。也许是他的胡子。
切得很厚的面包，烤得恰到好处。

用最好的太空牛制成的自制牛肉干。
油炸的虾味薯条。海鲜鉴赏家最喜欢的垃圾食品！
宇宙中最好的葡萄干。不知道为什么。
自制葡萄干，是所有葡萄中最好的。
抽完的糖烟的烟屁股。可以吃！
抽完的糖烟的烟屁股。闻起来像尼古丁...？
一口大小的奶酪点心，会在你的嘴里嗡嗡作响。
一种非常湿润的点心蛋糕，像被核弹轰过一样的好吃。
一个充满能量的能量棒，如果你不是电气人，你可能不应该吃这个。
A favourite amongst the terminally angry.
The angriest of all peanut flavours.
Oddly bitter for a sweet treat.
Where there's smoke, there's not necessarily fire- sometimes it's just BBQ sauce.
An ill-fated attempt at trail mix, banned in 6 sectors. Yearly lobbying to overturn is denied not because the apples are toxic, but because they keep evading the ban.
Legally, we cannot say that these won't melt in your hands.
Stuffed with sugary sweet caramel, making them a diabetic's worst nightmare.
Eine köstliche Begleitung zu Ihrem Lieblingsbier.
Beloved by small children and aliens alike.
The official candy of clowns everywhere. Honk honk!
Filled with one of four delicious flavours!
A pack of Sweetie's brand premium pistacios.
A pack of roasted sunflower seeds. Beloved by space russians and babushka alike.
Homemade roasted sunflower seeds in a paper cup. A healthy and filling snack to nibble as you watch people pass.
Triangular corn chips. They do seem a bit bland but would probably go well with some kind of dipping sauce.
Which came first, ranch or cool ranch?
It has the salsa baked in, so you don't need dip.
Notorious for helping cover everything you touch in orange cheese dust.
The only flavour that actually tastes spicy like proper nachos.
Filled with one of four delicious flavours!
你很有胆量，孩子，有胆量！
如果没有水，你可以用眼泪代替。
A savory dish of alien wing wang in soy.
想想看，植物学家会用这个把你打死的。
神秘的是，你为什么不吃呢？
一个五级警报的德克萨斯辣椒！
这冰冷的玩意几乎没有液体！
A delicious stew of meat, chiles, and salty, salty clown tears.
这是一道美味的汤，里面有面皮和大块猴肉，炖得恰到好处，汤的味道微微有点像香蕉。
喝这个感觉像是吸血鬼！一个番茄吸血鬼……
A delicious and hearty mushroom soup.
等等，你再说一遍怎么拼……？
Jello gelatin, from Alfred Hubbard's cookbook.
A nice and warm stew. Healthy and strong.
好得足以让一个成年的哑剧演员哭出来。
A gastronomic curiosity of ethereal origin. It is famed for the minature weather system formed over a properly prepared soup.
A spicy vegetable curry made with the humble bungo fruit, Exotic!
A bowl of mushy bread and milk. It reminds you, not too fondly, of a bowel movement.

A nice mix of noodles and fried vegetables.
覆盖着美味黄油的面条。简单又滑溜溜的，但很美味。
